text: Goephanes notabilis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fairmaire in 1905.Biolib.cz - Goephanes. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Goephanes Category:Beetles described in 1905 Category:Taxa named by Léon Fairmaire
